  "notes": "120V US plug (NEMA 5-15) — requires adapter/transformer for European 230V grid use. Also marketed as 'Legacy BETA Series' by many retailers. CO2 sensor: NDIR type, accuracy ±50 PPM, range 400–2000 PPM, deadband 20–200 PPM. Fuzzy-logic PWM mode (5s cycle) available for compressed CO2 only — disable for CO2 generators. Sensor requires ~1 min warm-up for operation, 30–60 min for calibration. Factory default: 1200 PPM setpoint, 50 PPM deadband. Fuse: 6A/250V~; output relay rated 10A. Package dimensions 275×87×94mm; device dimensions not published."
